<lyrics>[V1]
 Sak ka duh ngaimi hla ka ngei, A ka tlanh cang caah, Ka Tlantu le ka
 Khamhbawi kong, A ka tlanh cang caah.

[C1]
   A ka tlanh cang caah, A ka tlanh cang caah, A min in kaa thangthat
   lai, A ka tlanh cang caah, Ka Khamhbawi min in kaa thangthat lai.

[V2]
 Lunglawmhtertu Bawi Khrih ka ngei, A ka tlanh cang caah, A riantuan ka
 laksawng sung bik, A ka tlanh cang caah.

[C2]
   A ka tlanh cang caah, A ka tlanh cang caah, A min in kaa thangthat
   lai, A ka tlanh cang caah, Ka Khamhbawi min in kaa thangthat lai.

[V3]
 Fiangte hngaltu tha bik ka ngei, A ka tlanh cang caah, Zumh lonak le
 tihnak an lo, A ka tlanh cang caah.

[C3]
   A ka tlanh cang caah, A ka tlanh cang caah, A min in kaa thangthat
   lai, A ka tlanh cang caah, Ka Khamhbawi min in kaa thangthat lai.

[V4]
 Kei ca remh cia inn tha a um, A ka tlanh cang caah, Zungzal ka umnak
 ding inn tha, A ka tlanh cang caah!.

[C4]
   A ka tlanh cang caah, A ka tlanh cang caah, A min in kaa thangthat
   lai, A ka tlanh cang caah, Ka Khamhbawi min in kaa thangthat lai.</lyrics>
<title>A KA TLANH CANG CAAH CH153</title>
